lly-product-tag.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=320\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=320\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=300\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=300\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"asus rog ally, front view\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/asus-rog-ally-product-tag.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch5\u003e Asus ROG Ally \u003c/h5\u003e\u003cp\u003e$350 \u003cspan\u003e$500\u003c/span\u003e Save $150 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Asus ROG Ally is a powerhouse handheld gaming PC, sporting a 1080p 120Hz display. Powered by your choice of a Ryzen Z1 or Z1 Extreme processor, this model packs plenty of punch. It easily handles the latest, most demanding games, delivering crisp visuals and smooth frame rates on its 7-inch FHD 120Hz display.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eBlack Friday is here, and Best Buy has gone big on its gaming and tech deals. Thinking about snagging a \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-android-gaming-handhelds/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehandheld gaming PC\u003c/a\u003e? The Asus ROG Ally just hit its lowest price yet.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Asus ROG Ally is now just $350 at Best Buy — that’s $150 off its usual $500 price. You can get the same discount on the more powerful Z1 Extreme model too, which currently runs you $500 instead of $650. It’s the lowest price we’ve seen, making this the perfect time to snag one.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-asus-rog-ally-z1-extreme\"\u003e What\u0026#39;s great about the Asus ROG Ally Z1 Extreme? \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe ROG Ally is like a gaming PC you can fit in your pocket. Powered by the AMD Ryzen Z1 or Z1 Extreme and RDNA3 graphics, it breezes through AAA titles and indie titles without breaking a sweat. It’s your ultimate gaming sidekick that\u0026#39;s ready to roll, and even Wi-Fi issues won’t slow it down.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe 7-inch Full HD touchscreen on the ROG Ally runs at a buttery-smooth 120Hz, making sure visuals stay sharp and fluid, even during the most intense gameplay. And with Windows 11, you’re not limited to just one platform—game on \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/what-is-steam/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eSteam\u003c/a\u003e, Xbox Game Pass, Epic Games Store, and more. The ROG Ally is a beast, ready to take on any game, no matter where it’s from.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"52b7-4c6d-9534d107cf1d\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-android-gaming-handhelds/\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"best-consoles-hero\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/best-consoles-hero.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=